title: We applied to Googles €150m journalism fund – heres what we sent in
text:
We applied to Google's €150m journalism fund – here's what we sent in 
The Register Saturday 24th October, 2015 
Digital News Initiative , funded by everyone's favorite news service, Google. 
The initiative's goal is to "support high-quality journalism through technology and innovation" and you are able to apply online for anything up to EUR1 million.
